`currencyservice-2`\n- **Evidence**: The pod_processes increased in `currencyservice-0`, `currencyservice-1`, and `currencyservice-2`, showing a significant spike during the fault period.\n\n### 3. Service Latency Spikes\n- **Detected Metric**: `rrt_max`\n- **Affected Services**: `currencyservice`, `cartservice`\n- **Evidence**: \n  - `currencyservice-2`: rrt_max increased from normal median 5452.0 to fault median 27248.0.\n  - `cartservice-0`: rrt_max showed increase from normal median 5153.5 to fault median 7543.0.\n  \n### Hypotheses\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"pod_processes\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-05\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant rise in node_memory_usage_rate from 29.68 to 42.25.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Node `aiops-k8s-05` showed an increase in memory usage rate, indicating potential resource exhaustion or system misconfiguration.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased pod_processes in currencyservice-0, currencyservice-1, currencyservice-2.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Pod processes showed an abnormal increase indicating possible pod restarts or crashes.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max increased drastically from 5452.0 to 27248.0.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Service latency spikes detected in currencyservice possibly due to overloaded service requests or internal bottlenecks.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些发现揭示了系统整体资源使用异常和服务层面性能问题的可能性。需要进一步调查以验证特定问题的根因并实施解决方案。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据所收集的调用链数据，以下是关键分析结果：\n\n### 异常调用链分析\n1. **显著延迟**\n   - `CheckoutService` 调用 `CartService` 表现出显著延迟，`anomaly_avg_duration / normal_avg_duration ≈ 14.13`。\n   - `CheckoutService` 调用 `CurrencyService` 进行价格转换时发生故障：请求被拒绝且有连接错误。\n\n2. **错误传播和类型**\n   - 大量“连接被拒绝”错误出现在 `CurrencyService` 使用过程中。这表明 `CurrencyService`（可能是其后端，例如数据库）在异常期间不可用。\n   - `Frontend` 服务多次报告 HTTP 500 状态代码错误，进一步确认下游服务对上游服务影响。\n\n### 核心异常原因推断\n- 数据和调用链拓扑显示，所有异常的根本源头是 `CurrencyService`无法正常连接。因为 `CurrencyService` 对其他服务的货币转换流程至关重要，导致了包括 `CheckoutService` 和最终 `Frontend` 在内的一系列调用失败。\n\n### 检测到的关键指标\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"checkoutservice->currencyservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"连接被拒绝或连接错误异常多次发生，无法处理转换请求；显著的平均延迟增加。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n通过以上分析，可以将问题定位于 `CurrencyService` 的高负载或不可用状态，该问题影响了多个上游服务的正常功能。建议检查 `CurrencyService` 的性能健康状态，重点关注底层数据库或相关的网络组件。"}
